jokes.joke: What do you call a cow with no legs? Ground beef!
What do you call a cow with two legs? Lean beef!
What do you call a cow with three legs? Tri-tip!
What do you call a cow with four legs? Steak!
What do you call a cow with five legs? A cow with five legs!
What do you call a person who is afraid of cows? A cow-a-phobe!
